@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ctypfz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(v0)
    tmp = wp.sin(0.25)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.80 / tmp + 0.69)) + wp.sin(0.03))
    tmp = v1
    tmp = 0.69
    v2 = wp.exp(0.26)
    data[tid] = v0
